AUDIENCE: I'm
leaving on the 13th

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:08.760
to go to Puerto Rico to
a central mountain town,

00:05:08.760 --> 00:05:15.270
Cidra to bring
solar lamps, water

00:05:15.270 --> 00:05:18.900
filters, and solar
panels, and solar panel

00:05:18.900 --> 00:05:28.380
kits to a certain sector
of a barrio in Cidra.

00:05:28.380 --> 00:05:33.600
So the idea of a filter that
fits in a luggage, because I'm

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:37.180
limited to what I can personally
carry-- three 50-pound bags.

00:05:37.180 --> 00:05:40.640
And I'm paying $75 for
the third one, two, three,

00:05:40.640 --> 00:05:46.560
whatever, to do that, because
the bothersome part for me,

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:48.390
this is not my background.

00:05:48.390 --> 00:05:49.710
I don't know.

